<div class="site-container">
  <section class="c-content-box">
    <main class="c-content-box__main c-content-box__main--text-focus">
      <div class="c-content-box__main__container">
        <p>Live or work near London's Southbank? We'd love to invite you to join us this Christmas time as we celebrate together; singing carols and re-telling the nativity story.
        <div class="st-button"><a href="#section:sunday-10th-december" class="u-btn u-btn--dark u-btn--centred"><strong>Traditional carol service</strong><br />Sunday 10th December</a></div>
        <div class="st-button"><a href="#section:wednesday-13th-december" class="u-btn u-btn--dark u-btn--centred"><strong>After-work carols</strong><br />Wednesday 13th December</a></div>

        <blockquote class="st-blockquote">
          <div class="st-blockquote__body">
            <p>Now this is real freedom - to be truly seen. What could be better for Christmas this year? A Prince of Peace who scatters our fear? Yes, God is the Maker - but we hide from himâ€¦</p>
          </div>
          <footer class="st-blockquote__footer">
            - <cite>Jonty Allcock; Wrapping paper</cite>
          </footer>
        </blockquote>
        <figure class="st-video">
          <div class="st-video__container">
            <iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCoMissionLDN%2Fvideos%2F1922895634392711%2F&amp;width=560&amp;controls=false&amp;mute=false" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" allowtransparency="true" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe>
          </div>
          <figcaption class="st-video__caption">
            Wrapping paper - Jonty Allcock / Co-Mission 2017
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </main>
  </section>
</div>

