<section class="c-content-box">
  <header class="c-content-box__header js-object-fit-container">
    <%=
      responsive_image_tag(
        {
          "320": asset_url("static-banner/christmas/london-bridge-traditional-carols_320.jpg"),
          "640": asset_url("static-banner/christmas/london-bridge-traditional-carols_640.jpg"),
          "960": asset_url("static-banner/christmas/london-bridge-traditional-carols_960.jpg"),
          "1280": asset_url("static-banner/christmas/london-bridge-traditional-carols_1280.jpg"),
          "1920": asset_url("static-banner/christmas/london-bridge-traditional-carols_1920.jpg"),
          "2560": asset_url("static-banner/christmas/london-bridge-traditional-carols_2560.jpg"),
        },
        sizes: [
          '(max-width: 1200px) 1200px',
          '100vw'
        ],
        class: 'c-content-box__header__img',
        alt: ''
      )
    %>
    <div class="c-content-box__header__container">
      <h1 class="c-content-box__header__title">Traditional Carol Service</h1>
      <h2 class="c-content-box__header__subtitle">Sunday 10th December</h2>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="c-content-box__main">
    <div class="c-content-box__main--text-focus">
      <div class="c-content-box__main__container">
        <p>At the heart of the Christmas story is a glorious message of hope and freedom. We would love you to come and experience it for yourself.</p>
        <p>On Sunday 10th December we'll be meeting together near London Bridge to celebrate, to sing, to hear the Christmas story.</p>
        <p>Everyone is welcome afterwards after the service to join us after for a small meal together.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="c-content-box__aside">
      <ul class="c-icon-list">

        <li class="c-icon-list__item">
          <a>
            <%= svg_tag('calendar', class: 'c-icon-list__item__icon') %>
            <span>
              Sunday 10th December
            </span>
          </a>
        </li>

        <li class="c-icon-list__item">
          <a>
            <%= svg_tag('clock', class: 'c-icon-list__item__icon') %>
